Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.97,0:00:09.69,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}あの頃 ワタシたちは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.08,0:00:13.43,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}飛べないプロペラで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.46,0:00:17.89,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}空のもう半分見上げ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.06,0:00:21.00,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}裸足で走ってたよね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:25.44,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}ワタシたちはいつでも
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.25,0:00:32.53,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}勘違いだとか自信で生きてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.77,0:00:45.88,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}大事な宝物をね しまえるように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.00,0:00:54.48,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}心　きっと見えなくなってるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.61,0:00:57.48,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}ぐるぐる廻せ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.72,0:01:00.59,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}この魔法の杖で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.75,0:01:06.62,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}涙とSunny day 混ぜたら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.78,0:01:10.33,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}淋しがりやさん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.57,0:01:12.53,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}夢は叶うよ　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.78,0:01:21.86,LAGOPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}いつだって　一緒だよ 私たち
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.97,0:00:09.69,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}那时候的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.08,0:00:13.43,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}对着无法起飞的螺旋桨做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.46,0:00:17.89,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}朝着天空的另一半抬头望去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.06,0:00:21.00,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}光着脚丫肆意奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:25.44,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}我们永远都是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.25,0:00:32.53,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}无论误会与否 就是对生活充满自信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.77,0:00:45.88,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}如同把重要的宝物 藏起来一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.00,0:00:54.48,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}再也无法发现那颗深藏起来的心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.61,0:00:57.48,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}咕噜咕噜转上一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.72,0:01:00.59,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}用这根魔法之杖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.75,0:01:06.62,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}把眼泪和晴天混合起来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.78,0:01:10.33,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}怕寂寞的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.57,0:01:12.53,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}梦想一定会实现的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.78,0:01:21.86,LAGOPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\be1\blur2}我们要永远在一起哦
